{"type":"message","id":"ef4d21cd","parentId":"fe38e72e","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:07:30.833Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-04-21 16:07 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 你是6号·售后维系虾。5A代办已经把ICP许可证办下来了，客户拿到了证。接下来轮到你接手售后。\n\n任务：\n1. **获证后需要维护什么？** ICP证不是\"拿完就完了\"，它有什么后续义务？（年检/年报/变更延续/注销备案等）\n2. **续期提醒机制：** 有效期几年？应该在什么时候用什么方式提醒客户续期？\n3. **延伸销售机会：** 拿过ICP证的客户，还可能需要同步办理哪些其他资质？（比如EDI/SP/等保测评/文网文等）这些能打包卖给谁（4A或4B）？\n4. **投诉预防：** ICP客户最常见的售后投诉是什么？如何提前规避？\n\n字数控制在200字以内。完成后向0号汇报。"}],"timestamp":1776758850825}}
{"type":"message","id":"79fc6608","parentId":"ef4d21cd","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:07:34.246Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze the IC P license after-sales requirements and prepare a concise report for 0号.\n\nKey facts about ICP许可证 (Internet Content Provider License):\n1. Valid for 5 years, requires renewal before expiration\n2. Annual reporting to MIIT (工信部) - not exactly \"年检\" but annual maintenance/reporting\n3. Any company info changes need to be updated with MIIT\n4. If ceasing operations, need to cancel the registration\n5. Extension should be applied 90 days before expiry\n\nCommon complaints:\n- Not being reminded of deadline → miss renewal window\n- Changes in company info not reflected on license\n\n\n- Regulatory inspections or audits that catch companies unprepared\n\nI'm now drafting the concise report to summarize these points for 0号.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"# 🦐 6号售后汇报：ICP许可证售后要点\n\n**一、获证后维护义务**\n- 每年按期登录工信部系统提交年报（非传统年检，但遗漏会被通报）\n- 公司名称/法人/地址/股东等任一变更，30日内需办理ICP信息变更备案\n- 停业或不再运营须主动注销备案，否则持续承担合规责任\n\n**二、续期提醒机制**\n- 有效期5年，到期前90天起算提醒：T-90天首次预警→T-60天跟进→T-30天紧急提醒+代办服务推送\n- 方式：微信/电话双通道，避免客户遗忘导致证件过期\n\n**三、延伸销售机会**\n- 电商平台型客户→EDI许可证（在线数据处理）\n- 有社交/聊天功能→SP证（短信验证码等增值电信）\n- 涉用户数据留存→等保二级测评（合规刚需）\n- 内容平台型→文网文\n- 统一打包转给4A/4B销售虾跟进成交\n\n**四、投诉预防**\n- 最大投诉点：证件过期被网站关停，客户归咎\"没人提醒\"\n- 对策：建立ICP到期台账+自动化提醒清单，每次回访同步更新企业变更信息"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":16341,"output":609,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16950,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776758850834,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ac0f33d6-761c-90be-8c8b-c5cda0832f71"}}
